data.description: Bring all offers! ~ Welcome to 114 Lowndes, nestled in the desirable and convenient Crowfield subdivision! BRAND NEW HVAC & INTERIOR PAINT. FULLY FENCED BACKYARD. Roof is only 5 years old! This one level home with attached garage, large fenced in backyard, and open floor plan is move in ready! The inside has been updated throughout with new flooring, new tile in guest bathroom and fully renovated master bathroom with beautiful tile shower and a brand new vanity! Newer kitchen appliances, light fixtures, outlets, and switches throughout. This home is turnkey and ready to go! BRING ALL OFFERS!!!
